context:
KR:
&lt;홍루.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Hong Lu.&gt;

KR:
&lt;왜… 물어봤어?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Why... did you ask that?&gt;

KR:
&lt;있잖아, 지금 내 지휘가 잘 먹히고 있지도 않고. 계속 너희를 되살려 볼 수는 있겠지만…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Whatever I'm throwing at him doesn't seem to be working, and while I can keep bringing you guys back...&gt;

KR:
&lt;…하지만.&gt;
EN:
&lt;... But...&gt;

KR:
&lt;…아니, 이 정도는 생각도 못 했지.&gt;
EN:
&lt;... No. I didn't. Not like this.&gt;

KR:
&lt;…그럴 리가.&gt;
EN:
&lt;... Of course not.&gt;

KR:
&lt;그건…&gt;
EN:
&lt;That's...&gt;

KR:
&lt;그렇게 해야 할 거라고 믿었으니까.&gt;
EN:
&lt;That’s because I had faith that it was the right thing to do.&gt;

KR:
&lt;…!&gt;
EN:
&lt;…!&gt;

KR:
&lt;자비 아래에 동등해질지니…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Under mercy, all shall be made equal...&gt;

KR:
&lt;수감자들의 힘은 천차만별이었지만… 나와 계약으로 묶인 뒤에는 모두 같아졌어.&gt;
EN:
&lt;By entering a contract with me, the Sinners' strengths were all raised up or dragged down to a similar level... despite the disparity before that.&gt;

KR:
&lt;맞서 싸울 상대의 힘이 불합리하다면… 같아지면 되는 거야.&gt;
EN:
&lt;If we're in an unfair fight... all we need to do is level the playing field.&gt;

KR:
&lt;그래.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Yeah. &gt;

KR:
&lt;다시 한 번 싸울 거야.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Time for round two.&gt;
